List of things to do
====================

Tables
------

- Add boolean flag "migrate" to pgsql_stage.tables.

- Add Oracle column definition to pgsql_stage.columns

Constraints
-----------

- Migrate only constraints for tables that are migrated.

Sequences
---------

- Add column with the Oracle currval to pgsql_stage.sequences.

Functions
---------

- Add a "state" column to pgsql_stage.functions

- Create a function to migrate "verified" functions.

Views
-----

- Extend pgsql_stage.columns and oracle_stage.columns to include view columns.
  These should be used when migrating the views.

- Add a "state" and the Oracle definition to pgsql_stage.views

- Create a function to migrate "verified" views.
